<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.9.2">
<l>ītē yāṉuṉṉaik koḷvateñ ñāṉṟumeṉ</l>
<l>maitōy cōti maṇivaṇṇa ventā</l>
<l>yeytā niṉkaḻal yāṉeyta ñāṉak</l>
<l>kaitā kālak kaḻivu ceyyalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>This is me taking you forever, my</l>
<l>effulgent sapphire-coloured one that touches on kajal [colour], our father.</l>
<l>Help [me] to knowledge so that I reach your ankleted feet</l>
<l>which I have not [yet] reached, making the time pass.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
